                     <interp inst="t18170115-140-person1014" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a carrier. I had the box in my cart, I set it on the pavement, while I was in the passage it was taken.</p>
               <p>REID. I am an officer. I took the prisoner and trunk.</p>
               <p>(Property Produced and sworn to.)</p>
